entries.femaleVariant: What a surprise – visiting hours canceled again. Those fuckers...
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="そんな汚い言葉どこで覚えたの！？" t="Who taught you to swear like that?!" b="" a=""/>
Hm, let's see, maybe my skull-sponged excuse of a dad who can't even get his own family to visit him?!
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="な… 何言ってるの？" t="What? What does that mean?" b="" a=""/>
Don't ask me to come here anymore. It's a fucking waste of time...
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="あなたのお父さんなのよ…" t="But he's your father..." b="" a=""/>
If he was a real father, he wouldn't have gotten himself thrown in jail! And then, we come all this way, and he can't even bribe the guards?!
